---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI for Nonprofits | Scott Armbruster" description="Reclaim 20+ hours per week with AI automation built for mission-driven organizations. Practical solutions that work with limited budgets.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">
          AI for Nonprofits
        </p>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          More Mission,
          <br />
          <span class="text-white">
            Less Admin
          </span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-slate-200 mb-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto font-light">
          AI automation built for organizations that can't waste a dollar or an hour
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          I helped a 6-person nonprofit reclaim 20 hours every week using tools they already had access to.
          No enterprise budgets required. No technical staff needed.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            Book Free Discovery Call
          </a>
          <a
            href="/calculators/quick-wins"
            class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            Find Your Quick Wins
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Common Pain Points -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-slate-900/50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Sound Familiar?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">
          These are the problems I solve for nonprofits every month
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Staff Buried in Paperwork</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Grant reports, donor acknowledgments, board prep, data entry. Your team spends more time on admin than mission work.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Tight Budgets</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Enterprise AI tools cost $50K+. You need solutions that work with the tools you already pay for.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Small Team, Big Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            You can't hire more people. But you can make the people you have dramatically more effective.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Donor Communication</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Personalized thank-you letters, impact updates, and outreach that feels human at scale.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17v-2m3 2v-4m3 4v-6m2 10H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Grant Reporting</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            AI pulls data from your systems and drafts reports in the format each funder requires. Hours of work become minutes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Repetitive Processes</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Intake forms, volunteer coordination, event follow-up. The same workflows running manually every week.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Deliver -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">What I Build for Nonprofits</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">Practical automations that save real hours every week</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Donor & Volunteer Chatbot</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                Answer common questions about your programs, accept volunteer sign-ups, and route donor inquiries 24/7. Trained on your mission, programs, and FAQs.
              </p>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Starting at $1,500 (nonprofit rate)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>24/7 availability for donors and volunteers</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>Integrates with your CRM and donation platform</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>Escalates complex inquiries to your team</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Workflow Automation</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                Connect your existing tools so data flows automatically. No more copy-pasting between spreadsheets, email, and your CRM.
              </p>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Starting at $1,500</div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>Automated grant report data collection</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>Donor acknowledgment and follow-up sequences</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                <span>Volunteer onboarding and scheduling</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 border-t border-slate-800/60">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Your Mission Deserves Better Tools</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8">
        Book a free discovery call. I'll audit your current workflows and show you exactly where AI
        can give your team hours back every week.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          Book Discovery Call
        </a>
        <a
          href="/implementation/how-a-6-person-non-profit-reclaimed-20-hours-every-week-using-ai-they-already-had-access-to/"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          Read the Case Study
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
